                    <cell></cell>
                    <cell></cell>
                    <cell></cell>
                    <cell></cell>
                    <cell></cell>
                    <cell></cell>
                </row>                
            </tabular>
            </table>  
          </p>
          <p>
            What do you notice about how <m>L(x)</m> approximates <m>f(x)</m> and <m>g(x)</m> near <m>x = 3</m>?
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
